videos.headline: James hauls in amazing TD for WVU
videos.description: Austin Kendall throws deep to Sam James for a 44-yard touchdown that would stand after review.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (James hauls in amazing TD for WVU) 2019/10/5

videos.headline: Texas picks off Kendall, cashes in with TD
videos.description: Austin Kendall is picked off by Ayodele Adeoye, and Texas makes it count when Sam Ehlinger throws a 22-yard touchdown pass to a leaping Malcolm Epps.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Texas picks off Kendall, cashes in with TD) 2019/10/5 SOTFULL

videos.headline: Kendall fakes out Texas defense for easy TD
videos.description: Austin Kendall fools the Texas defense with a fake handoff and walks into the end zone untouched for a West Virginia touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Kendall fakes out Texas defense for easy TD) 2019/10/5

videos.headline: Ehlinger throws to an open Burt for another Texas TD
videos.description: John Burt loses his defender to connect with Sam Ehlinger for a 13-yard touchdown catch.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ehlinger throws to an open Burt for another Texas TD) 2019/10/5

videos.headline: Ehlinger runs in a 13-yard TD for Texas
videos.description: Sam Ehlinger drops back to pass, but then takes off and runs 13 yards for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ehlinger runs in a 13-yard TD for Texas) 2019/10/5

videos.headline: Jamison fights off James to make incredible INT
videos.description: Austin Kendall tries to throw to Sam James, but D'Shawn Jamison makes an amazing interception to give the ball back to Texas.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jamison fights off James to make incredible INT) 2019/10/5

videos.headline: Foster's heads-up INT leads to another Texas TD
videos.description: B.J. Foster deflects the ball in the air and picks off Austin Kendall. Texas then takes advantage when Devin Duvernay runs in a 13-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Foster's heads-up INT leads to another Texas TD) 2019/10/5

videos.headline: Texas offensive lineman scores TD
videos.description: Sam Ehlinger gives to offensive lineman Samuel Cosmi, who works his way into the end zone for a 12-yard touchdown.
